# MR.12 — explicit exception for the operator-facing env template.
# The example file is referenced by dob_worker/README.md ("cp
# dob_worker/.env.local.example dob_worker/.env.local") and
# documents the BRIGHT_DATA_CDP_URL contract — it MUST ship with
# the repo. The actual .env.local with secrets stays ignored via
# the patterns above.
!dob_worker/.env.local.example
